import React, {useState, useEffect} from 'react'; // import DashboardSlider from './DashboardSlider'; // You can create a DashboardSlider component import MemberModal from './MemberModal'; // You can create a MemberModal component import Edit from '../images/Edit.png' import Icon1 from '../images/icon-img.png' import Image1 from '../images/img01.png'; import Logo from '../images/logo.png'; import Next from '../images/next.png'; import 'bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min'; import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'; import '../styles/dashboard.css' import { fetchOpportunities } from '../services/api'; function Dashboard() { const [opportunities, setOpportunities] = useState([]); const [leads, setLeads] = useState([]); const [qualifieds, setQualified] = useState([]); const [bookeds, setBooked] = useState([]); const [treateds, setTreated] = useState([]); useEffect(() => { // Fetch opportunities from your API fetchOpportunities() .then(response => { console.log(response) let data = response.data setOpportunities(data); const leads = data.filter(opportunity => opportunity.stage_history[opportunity.stage_history.length - 1].stage_name === 'Lead' ); const qualifieds = data.filter(opportunity => opportunity.stage_history[opportunity.stage_history.length - 1].stage_name === 'Qualified' ); const bookeds = data.filter(opportunity => opportunity.stage_history[opportunity.stage_history.length - 1].stage_name === 'Booked' ); const treateds = data.filter(opportunity => opportunity.stage_history[opportunity.stage_history.length - 1].stage_name === 'Treated' ); setLeads(leads); setQualified(qualifieds); setBooked(bookeds); setTreated(treateds); }) .catch((error) => { console.error('Error fetching opportunities:', error); }); }, []); function formatDate(inputDate) { const options = { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' }; const date = new Date(inputDate); return date.toLocaleDateString('en-US', options); } return (
